

Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/HeikoR/Vim-files.git ~/vimfiles

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

    mklink %USERPROFILE%\_vimrc %USERPROFILE%\vimfiles\_vimrc
    mklink %USERPROFILE%\_vimrc_heiko %USERPROFILE%\vimfiles\_vimrc_heiko

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update





















